## Locksmith Integration

Secrets are managed by Locksmith. Use `locksmith get --key <alias>` to retrieve them.

- If `LOCKSMITH_SESSION` is not set, `locksmith get` auto-starts a session and prints
  the session ID to stderr. Sessions expire by TTL automatically.
- Export the session ID to reuse it across calls and avoid repeated vault authorization:
  `export LOCKSMITH_SESSION=$(locksmith session start | jq -r .session_id)`
- Pass `LOCKSMITH_SESSION` to sub-agents so they share the parent session.
